{"tid":1275763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇P牌仔咁驚比人當做鬼，咁想甩個P","createTime":"2019-07-01T22:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T02:01:59.000Z","uid":28435,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8aafb6a8dfe7326985534c66016be3d64c74d9","tid":1275763,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:49:39.000Z","msg":"我地連登不嬲奉行「不捉鬼，不督灰，不割席，兄弟爬山，各有各做」原則<br />\n<br />\n所以新會員可以放心，唔會有人捉鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ef6a8d65d5cea22bac7242fef5a919561035bd","tid":1275763,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cdd93202eb6e83a38564414fcf4e6cb4206c61","tid":1275763,"uid":234182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:13:35.000Z","msg":"隔離衛報post個P牌樓豬肯肯定係鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作故仔出嚟呃正評，講啲嘢同篇英文報道完全相反<br />\n最怕係比人信以為真廣傳！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為篇報導係放大緊示威者嘅衝擊活動<br />\n對我地完全冇幫助<br />\n後面推post嘅都非常可疑<br />\n<br />\n好希望大家推post之前可以fact check左先<br />\n唔好再比鬼呃同利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得閒嘅話入去俾個負皮佢<br />\n好多人見多人正評就唔會懷疑內容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《衛報》撐學生71闖入立法會，批評警方失蹤設局，快過4點林鄭記招！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275439</a>"},{"pid":"67cef52d2ecf1b8706d2b45e2392012f16114a33","tid":1275763,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:16:25.000Z","msg":"參考嚟㗎啫<br />\n就好似見到警犬首先要合理懷疑佢哋唔係好人同毅進仔一樣，簡單嘅Default嚟啫<br />\n唔係鬼嘅使乜驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868060ac44d755c3ff52f02787e380d